value.title: Lindsey Graham challenger Jaime Harrison eyed to be next DNC chair

value.title: Rep. Debbie Dingell: Democrats need to examine why millions of voters supported Trump

value.title: Biden education secretary frontrunners have been critical of  charter schools, back teacher unions
value.excerpt: President-elect Joe Biden has his eyes on two frontrunners for Education Secretary as he lines up his cabinet choices, but his pick is likely to frustrate Republicans in favor of charter schools.
